														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2113626">
									

<p>And don't forget your chapter title &quot;Don't Expect Them to Thank or Forgive You&quot;, a line from The Mountain Goats' adorably cheerfully depressing song: <em>The Best Ever Death Metal Band Out of Denton</em>.</p>
<p>It's ironic that I used to work in Denton and had often seen signs up for TMG playing locally, but I only discovered them after moving out of Texas&#8230; Dammit.</p>

